  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to investigate postoperative imaging changes and clinical&#xD;
      symptom improvement in patients undergoing revision surgery for adjacent segment&#xD;
      degeneration.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
